--- !u!114 &1914615083
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1914615081}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: f4688fdb7df04437aeb418b961361dc5, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  m_Material: {fileID: 0}
  m_Color: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
  m_RaycastTarget: 1
  m_RaycastPadding: {x: 0, y: 0, z: 0, w: 0}
  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "<align=center><size=48><color=yellow><b>Ink Knight</b></color></size></align>\r\n\r\nB\u1EA1n
    s\u1EBD v\xE0o vai m\u1ED9t ch\xE0ng hi\u1EC7p s\u0129 l\xEAn \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng
    \u0111\xE1nh b\u1EA1i Ma V\u01B0\u01A1ng \u0111\u1EC3 gi\u1EA3i c\u1EE9u c\xF4ng
    ch\xFAa b\u1ECB b\u1EAFt c\xF3c.\r\n\r\nM\u1ED7i m\xE0n ch\u01A1i \u0111\u1EC1u
    c\xF3 \u0111\u1ECBa h\xECnh, c\u1EA1m b\u1EABy v\xE0 \u0111\u1ED9 kh\xF3 kh\xE1c
    nhau. Nhi\u1EC7m v\u1EE5 c\u1EE7a b\u1EA1n l\xE0 v\u1EBD c\xE1c n\xE9t tr\xEAn
    m\xE0n h\xECnh \u0111\u1EC3 t\u1EA1o \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng \u0111i gi\xFAp hi\u1EC7p
    s\u0129 v\u01B0\u1EE3t ch\u01B0\u1EDBng ng\u1EA1i v\u1EADt, \u0111\u1EBFn ch\u1ED7
    Ma V\u01B0\u01A1ng v\xE0 ti\xEAu di\u1EC7t h\u1EAFn.\r\n\r\nKhi Ma V\u01B0\u01A1ng
    b\u1ECB h\u1EA1, l\u1ED3ng giam c\xF4ng ch\xFAa s\u1EBD bi\u1EBFn m\u1EA5t. Tuy
    nhi\xEAn c\xF4ng ch\xFAa th\u01B0\u1EDDng b\u1ECB nh\u1ED1t \u1EDF v\u1ECB tr\xED
    kh\xF3 ti\u1EBFp c\u1EADn, n\xEAn tr\u01B0\u1EDBc khi b\u1EAFt \u0111\u1EA7u,
    b\u1EA1n c\u1EA7n v\u1EBD \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng gi\xFAp c\xF4ng ch\xFAa \u0111\u1EBFn
    n\u01A1i an to\xE0n \u0111\u1EC3 g\u1EB7p hi\u1EC7p s\u0129. Khi hi\u1EC7p s\u0129
    v\xE0 c\xF4ng ch\xFAa ch\u1EA1m nhau, b\u1EA1n chi\u1EBFn th\u1EAFng.\r\n\r\nB\u1EA1n
    s\u1EBD th\u1EA5t b\u1EA1i n\u1EBFu hi\u1EC7p s\u0129 r\u01A1i xu\u1ED1ng v\u1EF1c,
    m\u1EA5t h\u1EBFt m\xE1u ho\u1EB7c b\u1ECB ti\xEAu di\u1EC7t b\u1EDFi b\u1EABy.
    Thanh m\xE1u hi\u1EC3n th\u1ECB \u1EDF g\xF3c tr\xEAn b\xEAn tr\xE1i.\r\n\r\nC\xE1c
    nguy\xEAn nh\xE2n m\u1EA5t m\xE1u:\r\n+) R\u01A1i t\u1EEB \u0111\u1ED9 cao l\u1EDBn 
    \r\n+) Ch\u1EA1m v\xE0o b\u1EABy (c\xF3 lo\u1EA1i g\xE2y m\u1EA5t m\xE1u d\u1EA7n,
    c\xF3 lo\u1EA1i ch\u1EBFt ngay l\u1EADp t\u1EE9c)\r\n\r\nC\xE1c lo\u1EA1i n\xE9t
    v\u1EBD:\r\n\r\n+) <b><color=black>\u0110en:</color></b> \u0110\u01B0\u1EDDng
    b\xECnh th\u01B0\u1EDDng.  \r\n+) <b><color=green>Xanh l\xE1:</color></b> Tri\u1EC7t
    ti\xEAu l\u1EF1c r\u01A1i v\xE0 l\xE0m hi\u1EC7p s\u0129 n\u1EA3y l\xEAn.  \r\n+)
    <b><color=purple>T\xEDm:</color></b> Bi\u1EBFn th\xE0nh d\xE2y treo, gi\u1EEF
    hi\u1EC7p s\u0129 trong 5 gi\xE2y r\u1ED3i \u0111\u1EE9t.  \r\n+) <b><color=red>\u0110\u1ECF:</color></b>
    T\u0103ng t\u1ED1c \u0111\u1ED9 l\u0103n c\u1EE7a hi\u1EC7p s\u0129.  \r\n+)
    <b><color=blue>Xanh:</color></b> Gi\u1EEF nguy\xEAn t\u1ED1c \u0111\u1ED9 hi\u1EC7n
    t\u1EA1i.  \r\n+) <b><color=#8B4513>N\xE2u:</color></b> Gi\u1EA3m d\u1EA7n t\u1ED1c
    \u0111\u1ED9 v\u1EC1 0.\r\n\r\nVi\u1EC7c v\u1EBD b\u1ECB gi\u1EDBi h\u1EA1n b\u1EDFi
    l\u01B0\u1EE3ng m\u1EF1c. C\xE0ng v\u1EBD nhi\u1EC1u, m\u1EF1c c\xE0ng gi\u1EA3m.
    Khi h\u1EBFt m\u1EF1c, b\u1EA1n kh\xF4ng th\u1EC3 v\u1EBD ti\u1EBFp.\r\n\r\nN\u1EBFu
    v\u1EBD sai, h\xE3y d\xF9ng c\u1EE5c t\u1EA9y \u0111\u1EC3 x\xF3a \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng
    \u0111\xE3 v\u1EBD. X\xF3a c\xE0ng nhi\u1EC1u, m\u1EF1c s\u1EBD h\u1ED3i l\u1EA1i
    t\u01B0\u01A1ng \u1EE9ng.\r\n\r\nS\u1ED1 sao \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c t\xEDnh theo
    l\u01B0\u1EE3ng m\u1EF1c c\xF2n l\u1EA1i.\r\n\r\n\u0110i\u1EC3m cu\u1ED1i c\xF9ng:\r\n<b>\u0110i\u1EC3m
    = M\u1EF1c c\xF2n l\u1EA1i \xD7 M\xE1u c\xF2n l\u1EA1i c\u1EE7a hi\u1EC7p s\u0129</b>\r\n\r\nH\xE3y
    c\u1ED1 g\u1EAFng \u0111\u1EA1t \u0111i\u1EC3m cao nh\u1EA5t v\xE0 so t\xE0i
    c\xF9ng b\u1EA1n b\xE8!"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2180264, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
